segments.text: How much money do you expect in this position ?
segments.speaker: S1

segments.text: With my experience , I'd like to start at 3,000 RIB per month .
segments.speaker: S2

segments.text: Well , it is a little more than we had planned .
segments.speaker: S1

segments.text: I think you will find I am worth it .
segments.speaker: S2
